---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Refund Policy - OptyP" description="Refund Policy for OptyP professional resume and profile optimization services.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We strive to deliver high-quality resume and profile optimization services that exceed your expectations. 
        If you are not satisfied with our service, please review the refund terms below.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8">
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Refund Eligibility</h2>
        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-400">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4 font-medium">Refunds may be considered under the following conditions:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-3 text-gray-700">
            <li><strong>Timeframe:</strong> Refund requests must be made within <span class="bg-yellow-200 px-2 py-1 rounded font-medium">7 days</span> of the service delivery date</li>
            <li><strong>Service issues:</strong> Refunds are considered only if the service was not delivered as agreed upon or contains significant quality issues that cannot be resolved through revisions</li>
            <li><strong>Non-delivery:</strong> If we fail to deliver your service within the agreed timeframe without prior notification</li>
            <li><strong>Technical errors:</strong> If there are significant technical errors in our deliverables that materially affect their functionality</li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="mt-6 bg-red-50 p-4 rounded-lg border border-red-200">
            <h4 class="font-medium text-red-800 mb-2">‚ùå Services NOT Eligible for Refunds</h4>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-sm text-red-700">
              <li>Services that have been completed and approved by the customer</li>
              <li>Changes in personal preferences after service delivery</li>
              <li>Dissatisfaction with job search outcomes (we optimize profiles, not guarantee employment)</li>
              <li>Services used or downloaded after the 7-day period</li>
              <li>Custom requests outside the scope of the original service package</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Refund Process</h2>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          
          <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-4">Step-by-Step Refund Request</h3>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">1</div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Submit Request</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">info@optyp.com</a> with your refund request</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">2</div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Provide Details</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Include your order number, service details, and specific reason for the refund request</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">3</div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Review Process</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Our support team will review your request within <strong>5 business days</strong></p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold">4</div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900">Resolution</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">We'll notify you of our decision and process approved refunds within 7-10 business days</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-yellow-800 mb-3">Required Information for Refund Requests</h3>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-yellow-700">
              <li>Your full name and email address used for the service</li>
              <li>Order number or transaction ID</li>
              <li>Service type and package purchased</li>
              <li>Detailed explanation of the issue or reason for refund</li>
              <li>Supporting documentation (if applicable)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Alternative Solutions</h2>
        <div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-purple-200">
          <p class="text-purple-800 mb-4">
            Before requesting a refund, consider these alternatives that might resolve your concerns:
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-purple-900 mb-2">üîÑ Free Revisions</h4>
              <p class="text-purple-700 text-sm">All packages include 2 rounds of revisions. Let us fix any issues first.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-purple-900 mb-2">üí¨ Direct Support</h4>
              <p class="text-purple-700 text-sm">Contact our team to discuss concerns and explore solutions.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-purple-900 mb-2">üìû Consultation Call</h4>
              <p class="text-purple-700 text-sm">Schedule a call to review your deliverables and address questions.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-medium text-purple-900 mb-2">üéØ Service Adjustment</h4>
              <p class="text-purple-700 text-sm">We can modify the service scope to better meet your needs.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Refund Methods & Timeline</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Payment Method & Refund Timeline</h3>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto">
              <table class="w-full text-sm">
                <thead>
                  <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                    <th class="text-left py-2 px-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Payment Method</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-2 px-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Refund Timeline</th>
                    <th class="text-left py-2 px-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Processing Fee</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-gray-700">
                  <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">Credit Card</td>
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">5-10 business days</td>
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">None</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">Debit Card</td>
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">3-7 business days</td>
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">None</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr class="border-b border-gray-100">
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">Digital Wallets</td>
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">1-3 business days</td>
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">None</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">Bank Transfer</td>
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">3-5 business days</td>
                    <td class="py-2 px-3">Banking fees may apply</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Partial Refunds</h2>
        <div class="text-gray-700">
          <p class="mb-4">
            In certain circumstances, we may offer partial refunds for services that were partially completed or used:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Services partially delivered due to client unavailability</li>
            <li>Scope changes requested mid-project</li>
            <li>Bundled services where only some components have issues</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
            Partial refund amounts are determined on a case-by-case basis and communicated clearly during the review process.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <section class="bg-blue-600 text-white p-8 rounded-lg text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Need Help with a Refund Request?</h2>
        <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6">
          Our support team is here to help resolve any concerns you may have about our services.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div>
            <p class="text-blue-100">üìß <strong>Email:</strong></p>
            <p><a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white underline text-lg">info@optyp.com</a></p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-blue-100">üí¨ <strong>Contact Form:</strong></p>
            <p><a href="/contact/" class="text-blue-200 hover:text-white underline">Visit our contact page</a></p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 text-blue-200 text-sm">
            <p>‚è∞ We typically respond within 24 hours during business days</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>